
================================================================================
 For Linux, MacOS X, *BSD
================================================================================

** Wormux 0.8 and upper:
Extract the archive in ~/.local/share/wormux/map/

** Previous version (0.7.x, 0.8betaX)
Extract the archive in ~/.wormux/map/


With "~" referring to your home directory (For instance: /home/john/)
You may need to create some of the directories.

WARNING: .local is a hidden directory.

================================================================================
 For Windows XP/Vista
================================================================================

** All Wormux versions:
Extract the archive in C:\Documents and Settings\<user>\Application Data\Wormux\map\

With <user> to replace with your login name.

================================================================================
 For Windows Seven
================================================================================

** All Wormux versions:
Extract the archive in C:\Users\<user>\AppData\Roaming\Wormux\map\

With <user> to replace with your login name.
